articles.author: Bethlehem Feleke
articles.title: South Africa files genocide case against Israel at International Court of Justice over Gaza war - CNN
articles.description: South Africa has filed an application at the International Court of Justice to begin proceedings over allegations of genocide against Israel for its war against Hamas in Gaza, the court said on Friday.
